{"tid":1280584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警察到立法會指模及 DNA 鑑證、 三維激光掃描等方法搜證","createTime":"2019-07-03T04:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T04:42:24.000Z","uid":85406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"43ebca32e3b10b7efc3c4cb48fed318f5d943b9e","tid":1280584,"uid":85406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:31:01.000Z","msg":"警方今早（3日）在 Facebook 專頁發文，指警方就示威者 7 月 1 日佔領立法會大樓，昨日到立法會以多種方法搜證，包括指模及 DNA 鑑證，聲言會對非法行為「跟進到底」。<br />\n<br />\n警方 Facebook 專頁「香港警察」今早發文，指警方昨日（2日）派出「O記」指有組織及三合會罪案調查科、鑑證科聯及政府化驗所人員等，到立法會大樓各處進行搜證，使用包括<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">拍照、指模及 DNA 鑑證、 三維激光掃描等方法</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n專頁又上載多張搜證相片，例如在立法會會議廳以照片和文字記錄損毀情況；<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">在會議廳玻璃欄上套取指模；出動三維激光掃描；在走廊指示牌上，取下示威者貼上的貼紙和標語等。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E6%90%9C%E8%AD%89-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%8C%87%E6%A8%A1-dna-%E9%91%91%E8%AD%89%E7%AD%89-%E8%B7%9F%E9%80%B2%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95-%E5%B0%87%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92%E7%B9%A9%E4%B9%8B%E6%96%BC%E6%B3%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2590%259C%25E8%25AD%2589-%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25A8%25A1-dna-%25E9%2591%2591%25E8%25AD%2589%25E7%25AD%2589-%25E8%25B7%259F%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25BA%2595-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%25BE%2592%25E7%25B9%25A9%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%2596%25BC%25E6%25B3%2595%2F&d=ItsvLBlInL5d1alZeSWtsCWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=a0a6c068\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2590%259C%25E8%25AD%2589-%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25A8%25A1-dna-%25E9%2591%2591%25E8%25AD%2589%25E7%25AD%2589-%2